        "OVERHEAD_PERCENT": null,
        "EN_DIAL": "My name is Geranium! People often call me the Reaper Prof!/\nSlorm Reapers are exciting weapons you know... They have a soul of their own... awakened by the Slorm... /\nThere are many of them and each one has been forged for a Champion of Arah of the past./\nFor some, Slorm Reapers are items to collect, others use them for fights./\nGiven your incompetence in combat, you must be a collector like me ... You have merit! They are very rare weapons and very hard to find!/\n[hero].../\n[geranium]Ah... I see... You use it to fight.../\nThen let me help you... You're not using it to its full potential at all, look... *click*<Anim Blessing>/\nThis is it... From now on, your Slorm Reaper will become more powerful every time you absorb Slorm, isn't it wonderful? /\nYou will be able to find others during your adventures but be careful, they are very rare! Come back to see me as soon as you find your first one!<Reaper Pity>/",
